description:
If you're planning a trip to London, here on business or just passing through, Tube Map - London Underground from the makers of the successful NYC Subway Map app is a must. 

Getting started is simple; just select a station, either by using the search bar at the top of the screen OR by tapping on the map. Here's where your Tube Map - London Underground journey starts. 

Feature rich with over 1.5 million active users it's not surprising Tube Map - London Underground is award-winning. From finding a station, planning a journey to line status and so much more. It all centres around the iconic Transport for London tube map, keeping it at the heart of the app.  Download it now for FREE. It will make your day.

- Voted #26 in TechRadar.com’s Top 80 best free iPhone apps 2013. 

- 2013 London Transport Awards Winner.  

- Apps Magazine says ‘Tube Map gives you an advantage over the always-perilous London Underground for the grand price of nothing. A truly wonderful app’ 5 Stars.

Tell us what you think of Tube Map - London Underground. Your feedback and ratings help us develop an app you'll want to tell your friends about. 

What users love about Tube Map - London Underground:

• Official licensed map so you always see the latest version.
• Route anywhere in London. Places, postcodes, points of interest and tube stations.
• Map features all subway stations that support Oyster PAYG services.
• Walking Overlay - Station to station walking distance information overlaid onto the map. 
• In-app purchases - Remove Ads, First & Last Trains and Tube Exits. For a great saving buy our Bulk Saver which gives you all these extra features at one great price. 
• Tube Exits tells you which carriage to board so you're next to your platform or interchange exit point. 
• The world’s fastest route planner with line direction all shown on the map so you can track your journey. 
• LIVE departure boards and station information.
• Notifications* can be activated so Tube Map - London Underground will tell you when delays/closures occur on those lines important to you.

*Please note: whilst we endeavour to ensure that Line Status notifications are delivered in a timely manner we can’t guarantee this 100% of the time. There may be occasions when the functionality isn’t available due to technical reasons outside of our control. 

Don't forget to check out our other London travel apps. Download now for FREE and take a different route around the city:

Bus London https://itunes.apple.com/gb/app/bus-london-live-countdown/id480643687
myCycleHire https://itunes.apple.com/us/app/mycyclehire/id675076655?mt=8

Join us on Facebook at www.facebook.com/TubeMap. We would love to hear from you.
releaseNotes: We've fixed a bug affecting realtime journey durations.
